## Apps & Responsibilities

### 1. `accounts` app
- Login/logout views (custom template)
- Admin-only user creation (`/dashboard/users/create/`)
- User list (`/dashboard/users/`)
- Activate/deactivate toggle
- No public signup route

### 2. `projects` app
- `Project` model with all specified fields
- User-facing read-only views (`/projects/`, `/projects/<id>/`)
- Admin CRUD views (`/dashboard/projects/*`)
- Search, filter, sort, tabs (Upcoming/Overdue/All)

### 3. `dashboard` app
- Analytics overview (`/dashboard/`)
- KPI cards + Chart.js charts
- JSON endpoint (`/dashboard/analytics.json`)
- Navigation to projects CRUD and user management

### 4. `management command: seed_data`
- 1 Admin (admin / admin123)
- 2 Users (user1 / user123, user2 / user123)
- 15-20 projects with mixed statuses, priorities, categories, deadlines

